sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant PF as Producer Frontend
    participant NX as Nginx (login-frontend)
    participant BFF as BFF Producer
    participant FAS as FHIR API Service
    participant FDB as FHIR Database
    participant OE as openEHR System

    PF->>NX: POST /api/bff-producer/immunizations<br/>(Bearer JWT)
    Note over NX: Proxy to bff-producer-server
    NX->>BFF: Forward + Auth Header
    Note over BFF: Validate JWT &<br/>extract user info

    BFF->>FAS: Data + User Context
    Note over FAS: Split payload into:<br/>1. Personal Data<br/>2. Medical Data

    par Store Personal Data
        FAS->>FDB: Save Personal Data
        FDB-->>FAS: Confirmation
    and Store Medical Data
        FAS->>OE: Send Medical Data
        Note over OE: Store in openEHR DB
        OE-->>FAS: openEHR ID
    end

    FAS-->>BFF: 200 OK
    BFF-->>NX: 200 OK
    NX-->>PF: 200 OK
